Transparency
Protecting your data
Transparency notices
The Houses of the Oireachtas Service takes your data protection rights seriously and we are strongly committed to keeping your personal data safe and secure.
Our
transparency notices
reflect the circumstances in which we collect personal data, the type of data we collect and the legal basis for processing it.
Whether visiting our website or visiting Leinster House, your data protection rights remain our priority. This is reflected in our
data protection policy
, which outlines clearly how we comply with our data protection duties.
